item.title: Adding custome items to SOURCE such as d claws,wings,colorwhips,d plate? how?
item.dc:creator: @Surfr Surfr
item.description:
@Surfr wrote:

Rip the item from the current RS cache.

Convert to MPQ (So we can edit it)

Modify slightly (Because items are different on the current cache version compared to 317)

Set TSKIN, VSKIN and PRI attributes.

Save, and convert to DAT

Zip into a GZ

Load the .GZ file into your /models folder

Open up class8 (for items) and create new INTs for the item.
